data.description: Welcome to Valley living in this Beautiful Brick home. This house is well maintained and sits on a Great lot that is .23 Acres. Walk into this large living room that is great for entertaining. There is a second living area that you can use for an office or just relax next to a cozy fire. The kitchen is bright and inviting and great for hosting. Hang out in the back yard under the patio in the warm summers or make smores by the fire pit in the winter. You can park an RV in the back. There is a lot of room to put many many cars in the front. Walking distance to the River. Close to Old Town and Downtown. The freeway is a couple of miles away. Shopping and restaurants are around the corner. Don't miss on this oppportunity.
